# Done

Finalize a done-ready change: check G_ship gate, archive runtime state, and clean up.

## Invocation
```bash
slipway done
# or
slipway done --all-ready
```

## Contract
- Only call when the change has reached DONE-ready state.
- `--all-ready` archives every active change that is currently done-ready.
- CLI checks G_ship gate before archiving.
- If gate fails, show blockers and suggest remediation.
- Show archived change summary to user.
